{"tid":1393733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局聯署：追求公義，不違政治中立","createTime":"2019-08-01T07:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T09:40:43.000Z","uid":7438,"like":136,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"618b2044e6177de186ba67679db576114b3a85fa","tid":1393733,"uid":7438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:39:45.000Z","msg":"62名教育局人員給香港的公開信：追求公義，不違政治中立<br />\n<br />\n我們是 62 名教育局的教學和非教學人員，我們一直以來秉持專業精神，在不同崗位上為香港未來棟樑提供優質教育服務，並恪守政治中立和堅守崗位的原則；只是近月社會的情況實在令人憂慮，我們想在這裏以不違反政治中立的前提下，表達我們的意見和關注。<br />\n政府自宣布暫緩修訂《逃犯條例》之後，雖然「行政長官為此向市民致歉，並承諾會以最有誠意、最謙卑的態度接受批評，加以改進，為廣大市民服務」，但是，除了在 7 月初行政長官約見大學生不遂，之後就是以警力對應示威，政府沒有作出具體的回應或緩和民情的行動；尤甚者，警方處理示威的方法屢受批評，最震撼香港市民的，莫過於 7 月 21 日西鐵元朗站大批市民遭受襲撃，警方當時的處理方法和事後跟進不能令人信服，社會不穩日益加劇。<br />\n作為市民，我們一方面心痛社會的撕裂；另一方面，作為教育工作者，我們十分擔心連串事故會衝擊學生的良知和價值觀。我們期盼透過立德樹人，教導我們的下一代成為社會上才德兼備的一分子，堅守良知，做一個具備承擔精神、尊重他人、負責任和有愛心的人。因此，政府應以身作則，主動走近青年，傾聽他們對社會問題和現象的看法，樹立以理服人的榜樣，而不是用警力蓋過他們的聲音，嚴重損害青年人對政府和社會的信心。<br />\n政府一再表示以現行機制處理事件最為恰當，但現況已遠遠超出日常的社會狀況，現行機制是否能夠有效處理備受質疑。法治是香港的核心價值，因此，我們很希望政府能夠盡快承諾展開全面、獨立調查因修訂《逃犯條例》引發的連串衝突，以還各方公道。我們期盼香港能盡快從黑暗走出來，重建公正而安穩的社會。<br />\n我們並不能夠亦沒有打算代表所有教育局人員的意見，但我們並不孤單；我們亦明白公務員須保持政治中立，服務市民；然而，追求公義的心，與保持政治中立的立場並不違背！<br />\n追求公義，不違政治中立。<br />\n<br />\n太多圖，想睇嘅入條link睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1066169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1066169&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5zYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=af19519f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1066169&h=787d750c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1066169</a>"},{"pid":"d0d26fed1b74dc76679a9a93360390036a107ef0","tid":1393733,"uid":7438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8301e9585409b0d13eba97256aae741e14df89e","tid":1393733,"uid":7438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e881c1aab65fd7e45d9dcd5e1e63be2eeacf21c","tid":1393733,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"277c34a5d1e0405872e0929808080e0071ef04ea","tid":1393733,"uid":258611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:41:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31b6a777ccac5f2228cfb6ddbc9e1e5e521a9b09","tid":1393733,"uid":31296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:45:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e0a181401f441c1363b2f397eeafc9537c548ab8","tid":1393733,"uid":278524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c74354f4f6f024bd27cadbd6222ecaee16e23666","tid":1393733,"uid":287061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:49:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d72c34545d6f3e944f216651ec77cab58c94657","tid":1393733,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:50:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">追求公義，不違中立</span>"},{"pid":"de33d5be9f0f1a6ca02cdfad818af9783602606a","tid":1393733,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:51:01.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"939f89b20bdc063c5ccb138abc2fd1a95657502a","tid":1393733,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:51:25.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1647856078cd935af112982273fcf79d6ef309fe","tid":1393733,"uid":175119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:52:33.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"85163301ca61b461f890fc6c80e141595efa3679","tid":1393733,"uid":258567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:52:49.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"2b62b0907ff510f244ade2a1f0ed576413196a02","tid":1393733,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfee0d4d0cab1c8a394601782fd07c0407b4ae3","tid":1393733,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab92bd67b7cd6da3eb2b23b31cbd7fbf281d193e","tid":1393733,"uid":7438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:16:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebfd4da846a3d3b336dab439dd256dbfcf98ff9f","tid":1393733,"uid":7438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:16:28.000Z","msg":"好難推得起"},{"pid":"c636edf0b9e2d8da696c36ef99a1da08e3cc8b02","tid":1393733,"uid":7438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:16:39.000Z","msg":"哩排太多資訊"},{"pid":"60db8319f01fe39900d46e1a97ec0cc2ceb95817","tid":1393733,"uid":7438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fc65d5a1ba2742b61ff4cd729491eb4117b80e","tid":1393733,"uid":7438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f992a276353684abfebb6b91a1f5a1a3a2bc6b","tid":1393733,"uid":119271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:20:49.000Z","msg":"良心教學人員，突然覺得香港未來好有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb56a56b9f07ce891a02e9f68a3c9276c3df9c1","tid":1393733,"uid":18012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc5d023bce07ef1cdf3de27a49faaf9f6729cb4","tid":1393733,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebfd4da846a3d3b336dab439dd256dbfcf98ff9f","tid":1393733,"uid":7438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:16:28.000Z","msg":"好難推得起"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:22:47.000Z","msg":"倒不如&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5zYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=ce9627c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721</a>"},{"pid":"3455b5d543876257df8e15a2349c27d2b2d98644","tid":1393733,"uid":239250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"1aec3b0a9256965de9939df80cb0d18e40cfdee1","tid":1393733,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:27:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">追求公義，不違中立</span>"}]}